* VcnUnderlyingNetworkPolicy represents the Network policy for a VCN-managed Network. * *

Transports that are bringing up networks capable of acting as a VCN's underlying network * should query for policy state upon major capability changes (e.g. changing of TRUSTED bit), and * when prompted by VcnManagementService via VcnUnderlyingNetworkPolicyListener. * * @hide
